"msg":"衰咩都唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39e8fb251dd95670fdc6e93e684f27d8d2648e77","tid":1030743,"uid":95497,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:20:16.000Z","msg":"依個？<br />\n<br />\n求救，有小學老師煽動校園欺凌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1030008\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1030008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"913cfdd029b48a25d3352e835bc3a9877ab7c47d","tid":1030743,"uid":110832,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:20:54.000Z","msg":"求救，有小學老師煽動校園欺凌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1030008\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1030008</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b333a741ea6c8d5982680fe925b59d65bbbde4e3","tid":1030743,"uid":161143,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:21:42.000Z","msg":"隔離post copy 過黎//<br />\n<br />\n事源係我上年開始幫一個小五男仔補習 <br />\n本身淨係知佢係培正小學讀咗4年，今年先轉校 <br />\n佢平時都幾活潑同百厭，但每次提起培正/見到培正啲工作紙，佢就會好驚同好大脾氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近佢父母同我講番件事，我先知佢以前比同學打，點知班教畜無停止欺凌不得止，仲因為想佢收口而叫埋其他人一齊加入bully，逼到佢兩個月內轉校&hellip;. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打番件事出黎，係想更多人知道班教畜做嘅好事，佢地愈驚件事揚出去就愈要全世界睇清呢間小學！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋，想各位巴絲比吓意見，點樣做先逼到校方出黎比個交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我就咁聽完都睇唔過眼!<br />\n<br />\n事情經過<br />\n語言欺凌: 2017新學年，受害人(下稱X) 收到班上男仔(下稱李)匿名寫比佢嘅字條，內容包括恐嚇X，預言X嘅父母會死。類似字條一共有5張，已經令到X日日好唔安落。 X比咗字條班主任(劉)睇，但劉話只係一般紙仔完全唔處理，仲沒收咗部份字條。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n身體欺凌: 11月李開始打X背部。X同劉講，劉依然話唔想處理，話件事交比訓導(下稱黃)算。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個星期後李小息時又打X，X不適到當晚就要父母帶佢睇醫生(所以有醫生紙證明呢件事)。父母同黃講，黃稱上星期嘅打人事件因為已經一個星期，所以file closed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，話會調查吓今次。<br />\n打人嘅時候X有朋友見到，後尾訓導洗腦個朋友話無呢件事發生過，黃之後便聲稱調查後搵唔到目擊證人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nX 父母一路有搵證據比黃，但黃話全部唔成立。後尾黃聲稱打人事件證據不足，所以又可以close file <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (真係龍門任佢擺)<br />\nX父母搵培正社工講，社工淨係話自己就黎退休，唔想搞咁多野就無處理到。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩件打人事件close file之後，黃就帶頭欺凌X。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1.黃去X班房叫大家遠離X，X一時之間無哂朋友，精神嚴重崩潰 <br />\n2.黃係小息時段, 搵兩個低年級同學跟著X去廁所,X形容好似係黑社會一樣, 非常恐怖. 身心受到極大傷害(X亦因此嚇到唔敢去廁所) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.黃屈X寫影響校風紙條並傳開去, (X表示沒有寫這紙仔, 更不是他的字跡, 要討回公道) <br />\n4.黃恐嚇X如果再講大話訧要叫註校警宫王警長處分X<br />\n<br />\n真心想知，點解成間學校無一個人做到野? 本身打人事件老師好好處理就無野，但老師個個推卸責任，仲帶頭玩9學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n培正小學真心cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望大家幫幫手推post，等所有人見到呢間小學有幾醜惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd59aea5ea2a54bfa8bb1cb4c87d1872e9aee60","tid":1030743,"uid":229609,"like":2,"dislike":23,"score":-21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"係唔撚係,叫俾丁x欣偷電話既受害人息事寧人嗰條教畜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbbda6a672b00cffa02c339285c1c13a65cf934","tid":1030743,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:43:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05f42c09bf106c3b7226d856f97444adb08af87b","tid":1030743,"uid":83094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:43:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"790c1aa48ac2cdde378d70f168ef0c0bb80d7da2","tid":1030743,"uid":204531,"like":0,"dislike":18,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:44:51.000Z","msg":"幾靚仔"},{"pid":"73c4270d999d4406a4f636b6d1551d995222f0fc","tid":1030743,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"238f1375ade5e330598483d0b313ca75d9802b0e","tid":1030743,"uid":234219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba8be36605e16229e6249e95deda83161f149959","tid":1030743,"uid":236368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b7b0fab18c1794f3dfbb2a969216ca0fc3cc996","tid":1030743,"uid":173848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:37:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"980b4f59d49d2d72d0df30defc6850d877196127","tid":1030743,"uid":49363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84afdd0d6a9e3567902a5383fcbdfe67411c70f1","tid":1030743,"uid":50790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:05:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2da457fb83a3615d13171102a51999da1277730","tid":1030743,"uid":173480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:10:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5933d118347479927b32a1c64924e8022dfd37a1","tid":1030743,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd24bb07c80ba692856b08b54289dc984ff520d","tid":1030743,"uid":105931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:15:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd632cd0df454e0b0a126bc7fdd20facb8b5c9f3","tid":1030743,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T13:24:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc2e570be82c40c002576c236ae282bae0f9579","ti